  stimulus_text = 'The passage below is adapted from a science textbook discussing the process of photosynthesis. \begin{align*} \text{Carbon dioxide} + \text{Water} + \text{Sunlight} \rightarrow \text{Sugar} + \text{Oxygen} \end{align*} This equation shows that the process of photosynthesis, which plants use to create their own food, results in the production of sugar and oxygen. The sugar is used by the plant for growth and energy, while the oxygen is released into the atmosphere.',
