  stimulus_text = 'The article states that the "authors'' main goal is to find an effective and efficient approach to teaching a specific skill." The authors argue that the approach is especially effective when "applied in the classroom to help students learn a new skill." However, the authors claim that using this new approach can be "challenging for instructors because it requires a new way of thinking about instruction." The article concludes by saying that this new approach is "likely to become more prevalent in education in the future".',
